data.description:
Discover the luxury and comfort in this fully renovated villa, nestled in one of the most sought-after 55+ communities in Delray Beach. This exceptional 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is being sold furnished, boasts an open floor plan, beautifully accented with new soft-close cabinets, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and custom built-in pantry. Every detail has been carefully considered, from the contemporary light fixtures to the fresh paint throughout, creating a modern and welcoming ambiance. Safety and convenience are paramount, evidenced by the new hurricane impact windows & doors, a keyless entry front door lock, and a new garage door opener. The home also features a brand new, efficient washer and dryer, new A/C unit, and a new roof, ensuring both (more)... comfort and durability. The exterior of the villa is just as impressive with an enlarged driveway newly poured concrete, providing extra parking & new landscaping. The garage, freshly painted, includes convenient pull-down stairs leading to additional storage space with plywood flooring. Perhaps one of the great features of this home is the screened in patio, offering serene lake views, making it the perfect retreat for relaxation or entertaining guests. Low HOA includes basic cable, alarm, lawn care, trash removal. 
Residents of this community enjoy access to many amenities in the newly remodeled clubhouse, which includes a library, card room, exercise room, and an arts & crafts room. Outdoor activities abound with two swimming pools, a hot tub, tennis courts, pickleball, shuffleboard, and two lighted bocce courts. Health and wellness are fostered through daily activities such as yoga, Tai Chi, and water aerobics, plus a social director and on-site manager. 
Located just 7 miles from the beach, this villa is perfectly situated close to the vibrant downtown Delray and a wide array of shops and restaurants. This home is not just a residence but a gateway to a lifestyle filled with luxury, convenience, and endless social and recreational opportunities.
